{"meta":{"authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}],"title":"","dates":{"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:07:35 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:07:35 UTC"}},"nodes":[{"index":0,"parent_index":-1,"body":"<p class=\"Paragraph\">The positive form of adjectives is formed by adding <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པོ་</span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་</span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མོ་</span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མ་</span> to the short form (xxlink above) of the adjective, or by doubling up the short form (in the case of adjectives like (<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆུང་ཆུང་</span>).</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Examples of the long form of adjectives are: <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སྐྱིད་པོ་</span> &ldquo;pleasant,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དཀར་པོ་</span> &ldquo;white,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གསལ་པོ་</span> &ldquo;clear,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མང་པོ་</span> &ldquo;many,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སྟོང་པ་</span> &ldquo;empty,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཙོག་པ་</span> &ldquo;dirty&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གཙང་མ་</span> &ldquo;clean,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གསར་པ་</span> &ldquo;new,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྙིང་པ་</span> &ldquo;old,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མངར་མོ་</span> &ldquo;sweet,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གྲང་མོ་</span> &ldquo;cold,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཐུང་ཐུང་</span> &ldquo;short,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆུང་ཆུང་</span> &ldquo;small,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལེབ་ལེབ་</span> &ldquo;flat,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སྒོར་སྒོར་</span> &ldquo;round, circular,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རིལ་རིལ་</span> &ldquo;spherical, cylindrical,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཐང་ཐང་</span> &ldquo;healthy,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉུང་ཉུང་</span> &ldquo;few,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སོབ་སོབ་</span> &ldquo;soft,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལྷོད་ལྷོད་</span> &ldquo;relaxed,&rdquo; etc.</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Certain adjectives are formed by means of an expression comprising a substantive followed by an adjective such as <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཚ་པོ་</span> &ldquo;hot&rdquo; (often pejorative), <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆེན་པོ་</span> &ldquo;big,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བདེ་པོ་</span> &ldquo;well,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དོད་པོ་</span> &ldquo;shape, appearance,&rdquo; etc.</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Examples of these are: <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སེམས་བཟང་པོ་</span> &ldquo;kind,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལག་པ་དམ་པོ་</span> &ldquo;greedy,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཇུས་གཏོགས་ཚ་བོ་</span> &ldquo;curious,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གཡོ་སྒྱུ་ཚ་པོ་</span> &ldquo;hypocritical,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཧམ་པ་ཚ་པོ་</span> &ldquo;arrogant, brutal,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཞེད་སྣང་ཚ་པོ་</span> &ldquo;scary, terrible,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཐག་ཉེ་པོ་</span> &ldquo;close, near,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མངོན་གསལ་དོད་པོ་</span> &ldquo;manifest, obvious,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལྟ་བཟོ་དོད་པོ་</span> &ldquo;superb,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གཙང་སྦྲ་དོད་པོ་</span> &ldquo;impeccable,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བློ་ཁོག་ཆེན་པོ་</span> &ldquo;brave,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སྟབས་བདེ་པོ་</span> &ldquo;convenient.&rdquo;</p>","title":""}]}